overview:
Synora Inc is a leading global IT services and consulting company offering the best industry-specific solutions, strategic outsourcing, offshore model that helps our clients achieve rapid development, world-class quality and reduced costs.

At Synora, we believe our value is based on our distinctiveness and our culture. We are not like most other IT consulting firms. Our behavior and values are defined by our core ideology. This is the essence of our guiding principles. All leaders at Synora have backgrounds within IT and digital industries and serve to help our clients increase business performance while managing risk.

Create Value - Immerse yourself into the client’s world. Understand, adapt, and deliver tangible results. Exceed expectations. Fiercly Innovate - Partner with clients to generate revolutionary ideas and creative solutions. Defy convention and use curiosity to fuel your imagination. Think differently.
